import React from 'react'; import CoinDrop from '../NeonThunder'; import { UpgradePlan } from '../types'; interface HomeTabProps { currentTon: number; minedTon: number; currentPlan: UpgradePlan; taps: number; handleTap: () => void; claimTon: () => void; setIsUpgradePopupOpen: (isOpen: boolean) => void; isMining: boolean; isShaking: boolean; showCoinDrop: boolean; } const HomeTab: React.FC = ({ currentTon, minedTon, currentPlan, taps, handleTap, claimTon, setIsUpgradePopupOpen, isMining, isShaking, showCoinDrop, }) => (
TON Balance
{currentTon.toFixed(6)} TON
SHIB
SHIB
0.00 SHIB
{minedTon.toFixed(6)} TON
Mined (Unclaimed)
Hashrate: {currentPlan.hashrate}
Taps: {taps}
Daily Return: {currentPlan.dailyReturn} TON
Current Plan: {currentPlan.name}
); export default HomeTab;
